Rails Boost installed!

Boost adds MCP introspection tools to your rails_ai_build agent:

  application_info   — versions, gems, convention profile
  list_routes        — HTTP routes
  database_schema    — tables and columns
  list_rake_tasks    — rake / rails -T tasks
  read_settings      — safe config keys (dot notation)
  read_logs          — tail development logs
  search_rails_docs  — version-aware Rails Guides links

Next steps:

  1. Restart your Rails server
  2. Point your MCP client at POST /rails_ai_build/mcp
  3. See docs/FRAMEWORK_PARITY_ROADMAP.md for the full parity plan

Docs: https://github.com/shahnawaz-ror/Rails-Ai-Build
